    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>The Grave-Construct is an abomination assembled from grave-stones and bones, held together by dark Rot magic — humanoid but terribly wrong, partially incorporeal, phasing in and out of visibility. It stands as the final guardian of the Emberwell's seed chamber, animated by Grafvitnir's command and programmed with a single purpose: protect the seed. Its Grave Smash and Rot Pulse are formidable, and its Root-Bound nature means it cannot be lured from its ward. When its Stamina drops, its Undying Purpose only makes it more dangerous.</p>",
